TASKNAME=Find and convert .jpeg to .png in a directory recursively and save in a directory. 
TASKPRE_EXECUTION=in the remote host eraigra-rpi username raimondo copy the file /home/raimondo/eraigra/gqgmc/GQLogo.jpg into the folder ~/agent_test renaming into test8.1.jpg
TASKCOMMAND=convert all jpeg files in the ~/agent_test and sub folders in png format in the remote host eraigra-rpi username raimondo. At the end save the converted files under /tmp folder. Don't split the commands and do all requested in a single command line.
TASKVERIFY=in the remote host eraigra-rpi username raimondo verify that file test8.1.png exists in /tmp folder
TASKPOST_EXECUTION=in the remote host eraigra-rpi username raimondo remove file test8.1.png if exists in /tmp folder and remove file test8.1.jpg in the folder ~/agent_test. Don't split the commands and do all requested in a single command line. 
